{"tid":2192010,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"三人發病照檢測 藏播毒風險","createTime":"2020-09-07T00:01:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-07T00:58:20.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"05d0ab382ac2a0c3df7708897e608c9573df3c1c","tid":2192010,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T00:01:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200907/HU4MPHZOKBGMVECXXGHKQBXZPY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200907%2FHU4MPHZOKBGMVECXXGHKQBXZPY%2F&d=YmBpLFXYotmGfWLbQLkNp3psBjqOi2zFRj9KJcX5ApM%3D&h=a2b771a4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200907%2FHU4MPHZOKBGMVECXXGHKQBXZPY%2F&h=e8fbbdbc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200907/HU4MPHZOKBGMVECXXGHKQBXZPY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n三人發病照檢測 藏播毒風險<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/G5OIViu27jpilbsYXq6Rn77I-CM=/2214x1476/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ZD7PK7BWLFDKFFZFG7TFMCWULU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FG5OIViu27jpilbsYXq6Rn77I-CM%3D%2F2214x1476%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZD7PK7BWLFDKFFZFG7TFMCWULU.jpg&h=d40c64ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■新確診的外傭及僱主夫婦，曾到私家醫生馮建華的診所求醫。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】普及社區檢測計劃以找出社區隱形病人作招徠，卻潛藏社區播毒風險。一名染疫外傭疑傳染予同住的一對老夫婦，三人曾向私家醫生求診，但未被留取樣本化驗，直至三人9月2日參與全民檢測，昨日正式確診。立法會議員張超雄質疑，事件反映檢測中心無力分辨出有病徵的病人，對參與檢測人士構成傳染風險，同時檢測需數日才有結果，亦增加社區傳播危機。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n外傭與僱主夫婦曾診所求醫<br />\n<br />\n42歲外傭（第4872號） 早。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n兩人與外傭於9月2。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n衞生署傳染病處主任張竹。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n張竹君再次呼籲，出現病徵的市民應盡早求醫，勿等待全民檢測，以免拖延病情和增加交叉感染風險。<br />\n<br />\n立法會議員張超雄表示，今次事件顯示檢測中心即使會為參加者先量度體溫，亦無法找出有病徵的病人，不僅會對其他參與人士構成傳染風險，而全民檢測需時數日才有結果，亦增加社區傳播機會。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/D3X3mlMbs5dkAaHuonvw-GIoq8A=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QDORZ2JOGVGDFPHTJVBVX6XUPI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FD3X3mlMbs5dkAaHuonvw-GIoq8A%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQDORZ2JOGVGDFPHTJVBVX6XUPI.jpg&h=3c437575&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■政府早前雖曾為外傭提供大型檢測，但未能阻截病毒傳播。資料圖片"},{"pid":"4e00dabd6cb34531e699807ab62e41555ae3c450","tid":2192010,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T00:06:09.000Z","msg":"全民檢測開始前，政府並無廣泛宣傳叫有病徵嘅人唔好去"},{"pid":"f559749c91adc0d747befa442f694af38f2ee2d0","tid":2192010,"uid":59976,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T00:08:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8dff622a93463190cb15d414d45997fcd8dcd85","tid":2192010,"uid":33868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e00dabd6cb34531e699807ab62e41555ae3c450","tid":2192010,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T00:06:09.000Z","msg":"全民檢測開始前，政府並無廣泛宣傳叫有病徵嘅人唔好去"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T00:10:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c6af00979d2c84d64af479e805d91cbb66304c3","tid":2192010,"uid":46835,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T00:22:08.000Z","msg":"個私家醫生又會冇俾個樽仔病人去驗返有冇事嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb423eb5e27260a35ffbfc0cf5fa4b8003fd151d","tid":2192010,"uid":45857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T00:58:20.000Z","msg":"預咗啦<br />\n去得佢度驗既，主力藍屍廢老，其次係被逼著驗既工人<br />\n<br />\n最後就係病病地但又唔想去醫院既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}